TaskTable.Query:
SELECT DISTINCT
	parent.ParentAccountBK,
	child.AccountDescription AS ParentAccountDescription,
	child.AccountType,
	child.Operator,
	child.ValueType,
	'Parent' AS AccountLevel
FROM [TCSrc].[QM_Account] parent
INNER JOIN [TCSrc].[QM_Account] child
	ON parent.ParentAccountBK = child.AccountBK
WHERE child.Operator IN ('+', '-')

Tasks.TaskName: QM2 - Migrate with Query Source CTE

TaskTable.Query:
;
WITH Src AS (
	SELECT
		AccountBK,
		ParentAccountBK,
		AccountDescription,
		AccountType,
		Operator,
		ValueType
	FROM [TCSrc].[QM_Account]
)
SELECT DISTINCT
	parent.ParentAccountBK,
	child.AccountDescription AS ParentAccountDescription,
	child.AccountType,
	child.Operator,
	child.ValueType
FROM Src parent
INNER JOIN Src child
	ON Parent.ParentAccountBK = Child.AccountBK

Tasks.TaskName: QM3 - Migrate with Query Source Aggregation

TaskTable.Query:
SELECT
	OrderID,
	COUNT(OrderDetailId) AS LineCount,
	SUM(OrderQty) AS OrderQtyTotal,
	SUM(LineTotal) AS OrderTotal,
	SUM(LineTotal) / SUM(OrderQty) AS AveragePerUnit,
	SUM(LineTotal / (1 - UnitPriceDiscount)) AS TotalBeforeDiscount
FROM [TCSrc].[QM_OrderExtra]
GROUP BY	
	OrderID

Tasks.TaskContent:
-- PSTG1 insert new rows
INSERT INTO TCSrc.PSTG1_Account VALUES ('N-0001', 'NULL', 'New Account', 'New', '~', 'Currency')
INSERT INTO TCSrc.PSTG1_Account VALUES ('N-0010', 'N-0001', 'New Account 2', 'New', '-', 'Currency')

-- PSTG2 / PSTG3 remove rows
DELETE FROM TCSrc.PSTG2_Account WHERE AccountBK = 'R-4200'
DELETE FROM TCSrc.PSTG3_Account WHERE AccountBK = 'R-4200'

-- PSTG4 update rows
UPDATE TCSrc.PSTG4_Account SET ValueType = 'Unit' WHERE ValueType = 'Units'

-- PSTG5 insert new rows
INSERT INTO TCSrc.PSTG5_Order VALUES (71802, 110675, 959, 4, 0, '2020-03-06')
INSERT INTO TCSrc.PSTG5_Order VALUES (71802, 110676, 971, 4, 0, '2020-03-06')

-- PSTG6 / PSTG7 remove rows
DELETE FROM TCSrc.PSTG6_Order WHERE OrderID = 71794 AND OrderDetailID = 110674 AND ProductID = 876
DELETE FROM TCSrc.PSTG7_Order WHERE OrderID = 71794 AND OrderDetailID = 110674 AND ProductID = 876

-- PSTG8 update rows
UPDATE TCSrc.PSTG8_Order SET HasDiscount = 1 WHERE OrderID = 71794 AND OrderDetailID = 110670 AND ProductID = 712

-- PSTG9 update value on ignored columns
UPDATE TCSrc.PSTG9_Account SET ValueType = 'Unit' WHERE ValueType = 'Units'

-- PSTG10 update value along with new datetime
UPDATE TCSrc.PSTG10_Order SET HasDiscount = 1, LastModifiedDate = '2020-03-07' WHERE OrderQty >= 7
